{"tid":344991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬 巴塞? 巴黎?","createTime":"2017-08-02T16:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T17:35:57.000Z","uid":87396,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3274e95fc3bcd434eeba7a356f0f5d8b53a672e","tid":344991,"uid":87396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"日撚日起身第一件事 就喺睇尼馬係真轉會 定假轉會 <br />\n你老闆 日日睇到嘅就喺 每間報館報 尼馬就快轉會 (太陽報除外 太陽報好睇過CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果去到8月31日 尼馬突然講 :<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實一直以嚟 我都無比轉會新聞所影響 我只會效力巴塞<br />\n<br />\n我真係會講聲屌你老媽子咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我嚟啲花生友都幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果尼馬轉會巴黎 踢到屎咁嘅樣 大把巴打一定出泥抽水抽到乾塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果尼馬踢到值身價(利申:本人其實覺得除左施丹真係值7千幾萬之外 連丙朗都唔值9千幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 班巴塞嘅球迷又會講咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十分期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8bf6450f9365897ab13ed7ece45c874a9e877e","tid":344991,"uid":35547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多 泥你老母先"},{"pid":"4c0b2ef47bc6342afe8ad55e6a2e2cee64b834a5","tid":344991,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"拎法甲同西甲比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?差幾皮<br />\n好難踢唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb6b82bc148c98d4e43bac15ce9f22a319d3035","tid":344991,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"阿朗都唔值9千幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54665384b05f1a8855b3c8a4d555a3315741323","tid":344991,"uid":87396,"l